{"data":{"post":{"id":"e2dccbb4-7223-537d-9127-fbd41d07f454","html":"<p>前几天一直在努力回忆一个词：“正向努力”越多，“收益”越大……<br>\n复利，初中时学的数学知识：\nY=（1+X%）^n</p>\n<p>《穷查理宝典》提到：<strong>什么决定了一个人的成就、财富？</strong><br>\n<strong>最终决定你财富的是什么？</strong>\n<em>起点吗？<br>\n起点固然重要，但要笑着到终点，持续稳定的增长更重要。</em><br>\n本质：<strong>复利</strong></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/369a7/compound_interest.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"compound interest\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/78f2b/compound_interest.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/dce19/compound_interest.jpg 200w,\n/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/c1413/compound_interest.jpg 400w,\n/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/78f2b/compound_interest.jpg 800w,\n/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/ab4c4/compound_interest.jpg 1200w,\n/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/bc99b/compound_interest.jpg 1600w,\n/static/fe0ab96ddb1edcb4edbf1f62cf9b9f29/369a7/compound_interest.jpg 1632w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/2018-08-23/Compound-interest/","prefix":"2018-08-23"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Do you know \"compound interest\"?","author":"Jane","category":"thought","co